OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSupermarkets forced to     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpublish live fuel prices   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Supermarkets and other fuel retailers  
OL,6, will be forced to publish live prices  
OL,7, under a new scheme aimed at stopping   
OL,8, them overcharging, the government says.
OL,10,FIt comes after Britons were found to   
OL,11,Fhave paid an extra 6p per litre for    
OL,12,Ffuel at supermarkets last year as weak 
OL,13,Fcompetition let them charge more.      
OL,15,FUnder the scheme drivers will be able  
OL,16,Fto compare up-to-date prices online so 
OL,17,Fthey can find the cheapest option.     
OL,19,FDriving groups say the idea, which is  
OL,20,Fused elsewhere in Europe, is overdue.  
